citation: Proclamation under the Corporations (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2001 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Corporations (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2001

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 7(1) of the Corporations (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2001 fix 15 July 2021 as the day on which both references under section 5 (1) of that Act terminate.

13 June 2016

C. WARNER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

DR VANESSA GOODWIN

Minister for Justice

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 22 June 2016

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Justice.
